tagline.en: We are committed to promoting EOS in Japan and organize the developer to build the EOS ecosystem.
tagline.zh: 我们致力于促进EOS在日本的事业并且组织开发人员构建EOS生态系统。

introduce.en: JEDA(Japan EOS Developer Association) which establish in Tokyo Japan. Committed to supporting and building the ecological system of EOS in Japan. Assist DAPP project development and provide other EOS-based services. We will regularly hold online/offline and other format of event, to promoting the acknowledge of EOS .Holding the developing competition and give the reward to the excellent developer.
introduce.zh: 一般社团法人EOS开发者协会(Japan EOS Developer Association, 一般社団法人EOS開発者協会，简称JEDA)立足于日本，以支援日本地区EOS生态发展为基本，深度参与项目生态建设。积极组织线上线下活动，召集EOS开发者开发有吸引力的Dapp，并且开发基于EOS的多种服务。
